Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是来接上井草同学的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好长 这车好长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那就明天见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见
